original: There was once a rabbit who was feeling very hot. Desiring to find a cool environment, he decided to visit a river. Upon arriving, he encountered birds singing melodies. The rabbit joined in the singing, experiencing both happiness and relief from the heat. And so, the rabbit found joy and comfort by the river, in the company of singing birds. The end.
